Why It Matters!

   -


*Live Vehicle Tracking *You can see exactly where the vehicle is, where it
   is going, and the *actual environment* surrounding it.


   -


*Monitoring Rider Behaviour *Provides geo-tagged, time-stamped video
   visibility to review rider behavior when required. This ensures better
   transparency, accountability, and visual evidence in case of incidents o=
r
   disputes.


   -


*Last-Mile Clarity *Provides visual confirmation of delivery environments
   and helps navigate complex urban landscapes.


